{
  "stem": "4113.1",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "If we go to New York to the United States, we are going to be paupers.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We just as well stay here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And they stayed there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Joseph, Joseph Platnar.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was my mother's brother.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, we just stayed there until World War II started.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the war started in September, I was appointed prior to it, in school, you know.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was trained to be a warden on that street.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I was also trained to wear a gas mask.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There weren't enough gas masks, but since I was more educated and--",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The school, the Polish school, yeah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I trained, you know, putting on a gas mask and go into a gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was trained with-- with a carabin, and all that, within the Polish school.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so when the war broke out, it was around 2:00 or 3:00 in the morning.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There was a military air base in our town.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And all of a sudden, I heard the bombing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I rushed out fast to the street to force people to go down into their cellars, put on a little mask that they showed us how to make out of gauze, wet it, and put it around your nose, and chased the people down into the cellars.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And there was lots of flak coming from the air base, and a few of the German planes were shot down.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The German [? planes, ?] where the [SPEAKING POLISH] which were dive bombers coming down, screaming down.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It was something awful.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We watched it from the outside.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "People didn't want to go down into the basements.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "They just watched the show, because this was a little bit out of town.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And they destroyed that air base that morning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that was that morning.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
